“青少年模式”，屏蔽高风险内容。设立未成年人维权基金，对因直播遭受经济损失的未成年人家庭，提供法律援助和先行赔付。 为推动直播行业行稳致远，皮剑龙还建议，探索“直播+”多元化业态，引导直播与教育、文旅、乡村振兴融合，打造知识付费、非遗传承等正能量内容赛道。构建全面的优质主播扶持发展体系，优化优质内容激励机制，对传播传统文化、科普知识、乡村振兴的主播给予创作补贴。委员建议：直播打赏建立“消费冷静期”，设上限，无条件撤回！"},"attached_info":"CkEIuLewyNee3v1QEAMaCTExMzg5MjA1NiCM/7m+BjAAOFlADnILMTQ1NzY0OTYzNjl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"109 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-5323183a2054b673d61b0b799a5a878a_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"15_1741620136.964358","card_id":"Q_14453923349","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":14453923349,"title":"你认为读博最重要的是什么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/14453923349","type":"question","created":1741453193,"answer_count":15,"follower_count":33,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[19768],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"大四，博零，直博北京某top2。 最近一直在思考这个问题，想要顺利的拿到博士学位，甚至要求更高一些，成为一名优秀的博士生，最重要的品质是什么？ 长期如何做？短期如何做？如何从导师手里拿回主动权？"},"attached_info":"CkEIuLewyNee3v1QEAMaCTExMzg2NzI2NSCJ77G+BjAAOCFAD3ILMTQ0NTM5MjMzNDl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"82 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"16_1741620136.964999","card_id":"Q_447357035","target":{"id":447357035,"title":"个人所得税退税越多说明工资越高吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/447357035","type":"question","created":1614746562,"answer_count":276,"follower_count":1129,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[6471,25283,35864],"comme